WEBVTT

00:00:01.640 --> 00:00:02.640
Wanna go?

00:00:02.740 --> 00:00:03.740
To the beach.

00:00:05.770 --> 00:00:06.970
To take some photos.

00:00:07.530 --> 00:00:08.530
Oh.

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:09.680
That sounds great.

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:11.640
It's been a while since I used film.

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:14.060
Let me see...

00:00:14.590 --> 00:00:18.450
I'm off tomorrow and the day after.

00:00:18.830 --> 00:00:19.830
So...

00:00:21.330 --> 00:00:22.990
why don't you stay over at my place?

00:00:34.350 --> 00:00:35.550
How did it come to this?

00:00:36.070 --> 00:00:38.160
Since we can't just move back in together,

00:00:38.310 --> 00:00:41.470
I thought a sleepover would be a good way
to test the waters.

00:00:44.510 --> 00:00:45.710
A sleepover...

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:48.760
I told you before.

00:00:48.910 --> 00:00:51.480
I've always seen you as a friend.

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:53.430
So, I can't stay over.

00:00:54.390 --> 00:00:56.480
But we used to live together
as friends all the time.

00:00:59.130 --> 00:01:00.720
Back in high school,

00:01:00.970 --> 00:01:02.480
we had sleepovers constantly.

00:01:04.070 --> 00:01:05.270
Well, that's true.

00:01:05.380 --> 00:01:07.580
If we're friends, that's normal.

00:01:09.710 --> 00:01:10.950
Friends.

00:01:18.040 --> 00:01:19.790
I'm your best friend, right, Wataru?

00:01:23.570 --> 00:01:24.570
Yeah.

00:01:25.410 --> 00:01:26.410
Minato is...

00:01:27.850 --> 00:01:29.600
I like you too, so it's fine.

00:01:35.390 --> 00:01:36.870
Minato is my best friend.

00:01:39.120 --> 00:01:40.320
In that case,

00:01:40.810 --> 00:01:43.340
just listen to your best friend's request.

00:01:54.500 --> 00:01:56.720
Once these feelings overflow,

00:01:58.180 --> 00:02:00.530
is there any way to take them back?

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:51.800
"Countdown To Yes"

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:56.300
I couldn't say no.

00:02:59.300 --> 00:03:00.590
Even if it's a sleepover,

00:03:00.860 --> 00:03:02.070
it's only for one night.

00:03:02.510 --> 00:03:03.840
I should be able to handle that.

00:03:07.300 --> 00:03:08.300
More importantly,

00:03:08.450 --> 00:03:10.130
it's been a while since I've taken photos.

00:03:10.460 --> 00:03:11.460
I should just enjoy it.

00:03:11.820 --> 00:03:12.820
Morning.

00:03:13.340 --> 00:03:14.340
Morning.

00:03:14.790 --> 00:03:16.630
It's been a while since
I've said that to you.

00:03:18.100 --> 00:03:19.810
And long time no see to this guy, too.

00:03:19.890 --> 00:03:22.750
I brought my grandpa's film camera.

00:03:23.420 --> 00:03:24.780
Let's take some shots around town.

00:03:24.870 --> 00:03:25.870
Sure.

00:03:25.890 --> 00:03:28.370
I haven't taken photos for fun in ages.

00:03:28.580 --> 00:03:29.580
I'm so excited.

00:03:32.950 --> 00:03:34.150
Why now...?

00:03:39.630 --> 00:03:41.180
Whatever, let's go.

00:03:41.570 --> 00:03:42.570
Yeah.

00:03:44.510 --> 00:03:45.710
(Episode 5)
How's your grandpa?

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:46.990
I saw him recently.

00:03:46.991 --> 00:03:48.119
He seems to have shrunk a bit.

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:49.120
Seriously?

00:03:50.110 --> 00:03:52.300
I haven't seen him in forever. I miss him.

00:03:52.580 --> 00:03:54.820
He'd be so happy to see you, Wataru.

00:03:54.920 --> 00:03:55.920
Really?

00:03:56.140 --> 00:03:57.420
I'll have to go visit him soon.

00:03:58.080 --> 00:03:59.680
- When?
- When...

00:04:08.230 --> 00:04:09.430
This sign...

00:04:09.830 --> 00:04:10.990
It's got a nice retro vibe.

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:18.880
Ah.

00:04:19.420 --> 00:04:21.240
The color of that door is great, too.

00:04:21.940 --> 00:04:23.490
Oh, you're right.

00:04:31.810 --> 00:04:32.810
Looks good.

00:04:41.890 --> 00:04:42.890
Cute.

00:04:45.330 --> 00:04:46.330
Very cute.

00:05:00.010 --> 00:05:01.010
Oh.

00:05:10.010 --> 00:05:11.700
- Welcome.
- Hello.

00:05:13.530 --> 00:05:15.480
I can't believe this place is still here.

00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:16.770
This brings back memories.

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:19.400
Hey...

00:05:19.830 --> 00:05:21.470
What toppings should I get?

00:05:24.430 --> 00:05:27.790
Apollo chocolates, Skittles,
or Marble chocolates?

00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:31.260
Wait, marshmallows sound good too.

00:05:32.330 --> 00:05:33.330
Wataru.

00:05:33.850 --> 00:05:35.830
Your indecisiveness
hasn't changed one bit.

00:05:36.890 --> 00:05:38.690
What about you, Minato?
What are you getting?

00:05:38.930 --> 00:05:40.030
Just milk flavor for me.

00:05:40.660 --> 00:05:42.150
You've always liked that.

00:05:42.190 --> 00:05:43.190
Milk.

00:05:44.010 --> 00:05:45.880
I only ever get the milk flavor,

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:48.000
And with no toppings, right?

00:05:49.350 --> 00:05:50.890
You haven't changed either.

00:05:52.910 --> 00:05:53.910
I see.

00:05:54.200 --> 00:05:57.510
Maybe I've only been noticing
the ways you've changed.

00:06:01.350 --> 00:06:02.350
Ah.

00:06:02.530 --> 00:06:03.530
Never mind.

00:06:03.930 --> 00:06:05.230
- Excuse me.
- Yes?

00:06:05.460 --> 00:06:07.919
Can I get strawberry with Apollo
chocolates, Skittles, and Marble chocolates?

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:10.250
- And a milk flavor with marshmallows.
- Coming right up.

00:06:10.280 --> 00:06:11.280
Wait, what...?

00:06:11.460 --> 00:06:13.370
If you want them all, just get them.

00:06:13.650 --> 00:06:15.000
We can just share, right?

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:26.340
Minato, this...

00:06:27.340 --> 00:06:30.309
Don't take photos of
me, shoot the ice cream.

00:06:30.310 --> 00:06:31.620
Look over here.

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:32.959
- Yeah, like that.
- I'm looking.

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:33.980
Not like that.

00:06:35.290 --> 00:06:37.770
- It's fine, you don't need to shoot me.
- I'm just looking.

00:06:43.700 --> 00:06:44.700
It's good.

00:06:45.600 --> 00:06:48.020
Minato, eat up before it melts.

00:06:55.530 --> 00:06:56.530
Delicious.

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:01.290
I haven't had this in forever.

00:07:01.750 --> 00:07:02.750
I know, right?

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.570
Here, try the milk and marshmallow one.

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:11.880
Mmm.

00:07:11.880 --> 00:07:12.880
So good.

00:07:22.370 --> 00:07:23.570
You can have some of mine too.

00:07:24.130 --> 00:07:25.130
Here.

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:32.560
It's good.

00:07:39.670 --> 00:07:41.330
Yeah... that's right.

00:07:48.250 --> 00:07:50.070
We're friends.

00:07:50.180 --> 00:07:55.120
This kind of thing is normal, right...?

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.820
Refreshing.

00:08:30.740 --> 00:08:32.550
Wataru, stand right there.

00:08:33.940 --> 00:08:35.720
- Here?
- Give me a cat pose.

00:08:36.020 --> 00:08:37.020
A cat?

00:08:37.470 --> 00:08:39.440
- Okay.
- Hands a bit higher.

00:08:39.680 --> 00:08:41.340
- Like this?
- Yeah, higher.

00:08:43.760 --> 00:08:44.760
So cute.

00:08:44.880 --> 00:08:46.100
I am not cute.

00:08:49.680 --> 00:08:50.680
Mmm.

00:08:52.330 --> 00:08:53.330
Adorable.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:05.920
Sorry.

00:09:17.660 --> 00:09:18.960
Welcome.

00:09:19.060 --> 00:09:20.630
- Hello.
- Hi.

00:09:21.330 --> 00:09:22.369
Feel free to look around.

00:09:22.370 --> 00:09:23.610
Wow.

00:09:28.330 --> 00:09:29.990
- Wataru.
- Hmm?

00:09:30.060 --> 00:09:31.060
Wataru.

00:09:31.710 --> 00:09:33.470
Wataru's right here.

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:35.920
Found you.

00:09:36.460 --> 00:09:37.460
Huh?

00:09:38.820 --> 00:09:39.820
Well then.

00:09:40.768 --> 00:09:41.768
Minato.

00:09:45.190 --> 00:09:46.700
This looks just like Wataru.

00:09:46.990 --> 00:09:47.990
You think so?

00:09:48.980 --> 00:09:51.900
- Thank you.
- Thanks for coming.

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:53.480
Take care.

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:14.520
Those ice cream toppings...

00:10:15.750 --> 00:10:17.350
I should've gotten some too.

00:10:18.450 --> 00:10:19.720
Mine was good, wasn't it?

00:10:20.010 --> 00:10:21.010
It was.

00:10:23.460 --> 00:10:24.460
The ocean!

00:10:33.450 --> 00:10:34.450
Minato,

00:10:34.530 --> 00:10:35.530
let's go.

00:10:38.530 --> 00:10:39.530
Yeah.

00:10:44.730 --> 00:10:45.860
Wow.

00:10:46.390 --> 00:10:47.390
It cleared up.

00:10:47.670 --> 00:10:48.670
Beautiful.

00:10:49.580 --> 00:10:50.580
Incredible.

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:02.880
It's so vast.

00:11:04.850 --> 00:11:05.850
Right?

00:11:08.920 --> 00:11:10.590
Oh, this is nice.

00:11:11.010 --> 00:11:12.010
Hmm?

00:11:12.670 --> 00:11:13.970
Wataru and Mt. Fuji.

00:11:16.570 --> 00:11:17.570
You're right.

00:11:18.840 --> 00:11:20.600
- That's good luck.
- Good luck?

00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:23.920
Does a photo with Mt. Fuji bring good luck?

00:11:25.580 --> 00:11:26.580
What?

00:11:27.140 --> 00:11:28.140
Whoa.

00:11:29.280 --> 00:11:31.030
Make this pickled plum look cute.

00:11:33.370 --> 00:11:34.370
It is cute.

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:36.460
Yeah, I guess.

00:11:47.260 --> 00:11:49.200
A rice ball made by Minato.

00:11:49.540 --> 00:11:50.540
So good.

00:11:51.390 --> 00:11:52.690
You've always liked these.

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:53.920
Pickled plums.

00:11:55.340 --> 00:11:57.020
I haven't had one since we were students.

00:11:57.390 --> 00:11:58.670
The taste hasn't changed at all.

00:12:00.010 --> 00:12:01.010
So nostalgic.

00:12:05.430 --> 00:12:06.530
So sour!

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:23.500
(September 26, 2017)

00:12:23.570 --> 00:12:25.560
I totally bombed that photo contest.

00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:34.440
Me too.

00:12:36.360 --> 00:12:39.060
But I really think your
photos are great, Minato.

00:12:45.520 --> 00:12:46.520
Same here.

00:12:46.950 --> 00:12:49.240
I've always loved your photos, Wataru.

00:12:51.340 --> 00:12:53.540
That really means a lot right now.

00:13:03.770 --> 00:13:04.770
Delicious.

00:13:11.720 --> 00:13:13.020
A disposable camera?

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:15.630
I thought it'd be a nice change of pace.

00:13:16.540 --> 00:13:17.540
For a fresh perspective.

00:13:18.020 --> 00:13:19.620
Yeah, I like that.

00:13:21.490 --> 00:13:22.490
One more.

00:13:25.160 --> 00:13:26.500
This time I'll stuff my cheeks.

00:13:33.680 --> 00:13:34.940
The ocean is the best.

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:37.840
This feels good.

00:13:39.110 --> 00:13:39.490
Ready?

00:13:39.491 --> 00:13:41.609
- Closer, come closer!
- Here comes a wave!

00:13:41.610 --> 00:13:42.610
One, two, three!

00:13:43.180 --> 00:13:43.600
Nice.

00:13:43.800 --> 00:13:44.800
Switch, switch.

00:13:45.420 --> 00:13:46.649
- You know how to use it?
- Got it.

00:13:46.650 --> 00:13:49.570
Minato, look over here.

00:13:49.653 --> 00:13:50.993
No, stop it.

00:13:51.370 --> 00:13:52.370
Looking good.

00:13:52.550 --> 00:13:54.420
- Hurry up and take it!
- I'm taking it!

00:13:54.650 --> 00:13:56.300
- Come on, take the shot!
- I am!

00:13:58.450 --> 00:13:59.746
I'm already in the water, that's enough.

00:13:59.770 --> 00:14:01.529
- Minato!
- I'm not going in.

00:14:01.530 --> 00:14:03.050
- You don't have to go deep.
- Come on!

00:14:07.310 --> 00:14:09.690
The waves are huge! It's so cold!

00:14:15.790 --> 00:14:17.470
- This is great!
- Here, Minato, hold this.

00:14:18.070 --> 00:14:19.750
- Here?
- Just stay there a second.

00:14:20.350 --> 00:14:24.720
- Let's play: don't let the sparkler go out.
- You're on.

00:14:28.270 --> 00:14:29.270
I like this.

00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:02.950
Taking photos really is the best.

00:15:03.610 --> 00:15:04.610
Hmm?

00:15:06.370 --> 00:15:07.370
You know,

00:15:07.920 --> 00:15:10.560
I was really banking on this contest.

00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:13.030
It was our last one in high school.

00:15:13.900 --> 00:15:15.320
I thought if I didn't win,

00:15:15.690 --> 00:15:18.170
I'd just keep photography
as a hobby in college.

00:15:18.960 --> 00:15:19.960
Yeah.

00:15:20.340 --> 00:15:22.650
And I still didn't win.

00:15:24.010 --> 00:15:25.570
But an honorable mention counts, right?

00:15:27.450 --> 00:15:29.250
But because it was only
an honorable mention,

00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:31.179
I started wondering if
I could ever go further.

00:15:31.180 --> 00:15:33.080
Maybe it's just too hard for me.

00:15:33.800 --> 00:15:35.360
To be honest, I was pretty discouraged.

00:15:36.970 --> 00:15:37.970
But now...

00:15:39.120 --> 00:15:40.940
I want to keep trying a little longer.

00:15:43.970 --> 00:15:44.970
Mmm.

00:15:45.320 --> 00:15:46.520
You shouldn't give up.

00:16:03.500 --> 00:16:05.699
(September 23, 2025)

00:16:05.700 --> 00:16:07.520
The ocean really is calming.

00:16:12.510 --> 00:16:13.510
Yeah.

00:16:13.890 --> 00:16:14.890
I feel the same.

00:16:16.770 --> 00:16:18.540
I feel at peace when I'm with you, Minato.

00:16:20.620 --> 00:16:21.620
Hmm?

00:16:22.540 --> 00:16:24.770
That hasn't changed, then or now.

00:16:25.920 --> 00:16:26.920
Oh.

00:16:27.010 --> 00:16:28.456
Don't just take my picture like that.

00:16:28.480 --> 00:16:29.960
I just wanted to capture that moment.

00:16:39.210 --> 00:16:40.750
Ah, I see.

00:16:41.290 --> 00:16:42.449
The backlight and the
reflection on the water...

00:16:42.450 --> 00:16:43.610
The colors should be amazing.

00:16:44.330 --> 00:16:46.080
That's not what I meant.

00:16:46.280 --> 00:16:47.280
Eh?

00:16:53.700 --> 00:16:55.380
You had a great look on your face, Wataru.

00:17:01.430 --> 00:17:03.090
Stop taking pictures of me.

00:17:03.420 --> 00:17:05.800
Here, go on, get in the water.

00:17:06.290 --> 00:17:07.510
- Go.
- In the water?

00:17:07.870 --> 00:17:09.030
Just right there at the edge.

00:17:24.500 --> 00:17:25.700
I like you...

00:17:33.230 --> 00:17:34.590
I like you, Minato.

00:17:43.680 --> 00:17:45.200
Should we do another photo exhibition?

00:17:48.980 --> 00:17:49.980
Wataru?

00:17:51.550 --> 00:17:52.550
Huh?

00:17:52.800 --> 00:17:53.800
Oh.

00:17:54.090 --> 00:17:55.090
Yeah.

00:17:55.590 --> 00:17:56.750
That sounds like a good idea.

00:17:58.840 --> 00:17:59.840
Let's head back.

00:18:00.560 --> 00:18:01.560
Yeah.

00:18:03.910 --> 00:18:05.830
It's been a while since
we walked home together.

00:18:06.550 --> 00:18:07.550
You...

00:18:07.650 --> 00:18:08.930
You've been saying that all day.

00:18:18.410 --> 00:18:19.410
Wataru.

00:18:24.110 --> 00:18:25.110
That looks heavy.

00:18:25.510 --> 00:18:26.510
Let me carry it.

00:18:26.830 --> 00:18:27.830
I'm fine.

00:18:28.680 --> 00:18:29.680
Wataru?

00:18:31.390 --> 00:18:32.870
That looks delicious.

00:18:34.130 --> 00:18:35.830
Didn't we already buy dinner?

00:19:01.340 --> 00:19:02.490
Hey, hey, hey.

00:19:04.520 --> 00:19:05.520
It's this way.

00:19:06.670 --> 00:19:07.670
Ah...

00:19:33.600 --> 00:19:34.670
Wataru.

00:19:35.080 --> 00:19:36.080
Hmm?

00:19:36.120 --> 00:19:38.170
How many steps to cross the tracks?

00:19:40.430 --> 00:19:41.430
Five.

00:19:41.540 --> 00:19:42.540
- Five?
- Yeah.

00:19:43.110 --> 00:19:44.750
- Are your legs really that long?
- Hey!

00:19:45.670 --> 00:19:46.670
What about you, Minato?

00:19:46.790 --> 00:19:47.890
Eight steps.

00:19:49.260 --> 00:19:50.580
How practical.

00:19:51.210 --> 00:19:53.290
No, not yet.

00:19:53.840 --> 00:19:54.840
Ah.

00:19:59.250 --> 00:20:00.450
This really is nice.

00:20:02.120 --> 00:20:03.120
Eh?

00:20:04.170 --> 00:20:06.250
Taking photos with you whenever we want,

00:20:06.500 --> 00:20:07.820
eating good food,

00:20:08.530 --> 00:20:10.820
and seeing you look so happy.

00:20:11.540 --> 00:20:13.040
It's a great feeling.

00:20:18.980 --> 00:20:19.980
Two.

00:20:20.110 --> 00:20:21.110
Three.

00:20:21.610 --> 00:20:22.610
Wataru?

00:20:22.910 --> 00:20:23.910
Wataru?

00:20:23.980 --> 00:20:24.980
Four.

00:20:24.990 --> 00:20:25.990
Five.

00:20:26.070 --> 00:20:27.370
- Made it!
- Six.

00:20:27.480 --> 00:20:28.480
Seven.

00:20:28.970 --> 00:20:29.970
Eight.

00:20:30.340 --> 00:20:31.940
- Five.
- Eight.

00:20:44.120 --> 00:20:45.120
Wataru?

00:20:50.680 --> 00:20:51.680
I...

00:20:51.990 --> 00:20:53.370
Maybe I should just go...

00:21:06.610 --> 00:21:08.610
These feelings I have for Minato...

00:21:10.140 --> 00:21:11.980
There's definitely no going back now.

00:21:38.520 --> 00:21:39.520
We're here.

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:40.830
Eh?

00:21:41.550 --> 00:21:42.550
My place.

00:21:45.630 --> 00:21:46.630
Let's go.

00:21:56.560 --> 00:21:57.560
Come on in.

00:21:58.910 --> 00:22:00.140
Thanks for having me.

00:22:00.450 --> 00:22:01.780
It's just a temporary place.

00:22:01.830 --> 00:22:03.129
But if you're willing to live with me,

00:22:03.130 --> 00:22:04.450
I'm happy to move somewhere else.

00:22:06.010 --> 00:22:07.530
You're so persistent.

00:22:07.760 --> 00:22:09.550
I prefer the term "determined."

00:22:15.070 --> 00:22:16.070
What's wrong?

00:22:16.580 --> 00:22:17.780
Come inside.

00:22:24.370 --> 00:22:25.750
Aren't we eating together?

00:22:28.690 --> 00:22:29.690
Yeah, we are.

00:22:31.660 --> 00:22:32.660
Then come on.

00:22:46.110 --> 00:22:47.310
Welcome home.

00:22:50.020 --> 00:22:51.280
Thanks.

00:23:00.160 --> 00:23:01.776
(Next Episode)
Why do we have to be boyfriends?

00:23:01.800 --> 00:23:03.799
Can't we just go back to how it was?
Wasn't that fun enough?

00:23:03.800 --> 00:23:04.860
When I'm with you, Wataru,

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:07.060
I can really feel my heart beating.

00:23:07.100 --> 00:23:09.159
How do you know things won't
be better if we move forward?

00:23:09.160 --> 00:23:10.680
No, no, no! I can't.

00:23:11.690 --> 00:23:12.570
The things we didn't do back then...

00:23:12.571 --> 00:23:14.010
can we make up for them now?